      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>Notes relating to and manuscripts of <title render="italic">Castro's Cuba, Cuba's Fidel</title> by Lockwood. Included in the collection are ten tapes of a 22-hour interview with Castro. These tapes contain Lockwood's questions, Castro's answers, and Vallejo's translation into English. An edited transcript of these tapes, signed, and dated by Castro, is included.</p>
      </scopecontent>
